data.description: 'CURRENTLY UNDER CONTRACT, SELLER WILL CONSIDER BACKUP OFFERS' Assumable VA mortgage for qualified buyers. This Victoria has 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths, offering a split floorplan. The flooring throughout the home is engineered vinyl plank in all areas except for the bedrooms. The bedrooms offer plush frieze carpet. The secondary bedrooms can be found in their own wing, off the foyer. Enjoy a gourmet kitchen with Whirlpool cooktop, vented hood, wall microwave, oven and refrigerator. you will find the  primary bedroom located on the rear of the home  and is spacious and adjoined to the primary bathroom with a tiled shower, soaker tub, and double sink vanity.
